以下的练习是从IC 网上练习本转用的。The following exercises are adapted from the IC Webapp Workbook L15-1  Reading Q5, and Grammar and Writing section, Q3



\begin{enumerate}
\item This is an instruction label on a prescription drug bottle. 用英文写 1-8 是什么意思 。要是 你不懂 ”服药 " 请看课本第134 页 的笔记。（1）
\begin{center}
\includegraphics[width=.9\linewidth]{./data/RXLabel.jpg}
\end{center}
\begin{enumerate}
\item Date
\item Each day eat \ldots{} times, each time eat \ldots{} pills, every other time (?)
\item empty stomach
\item in the morning
\item before bedtime
\item when it's convenient
\item after you;'ve atedn, you can drink, sleep, eat
\item Medicine name
\end{enumerate}
\item 你送了你的中国朋友, 张英, 去看病。医生给他开了药。用中写下来 这种药怎么吃.（2）
\begin{itemize}
\item 1 tablet, 3x/day; 每日服三次，每次服一粒
\item Drink a cup of water when taking this medicine; 吃药的时候要喝水
\item Take on an empty stomach; 吃药的时候不要吃
\item After taking medicine, do not eat for at least 30 minutes; 吃药以后要等三十分就可以吃
\end{itemize}
\item Grammar and Writing 5/C. Answer these questions according to your own circumstances.  (1)

\begin{itemize}
\item 你每个星期上几次中文课？每个星期上三次中文课
\item 你每个星期工作几次？我每个星期工作很多次
\item 你每个星期运动几次？我每个星期运动七次
\item 你每个月洗几次衣服？我每个月洗五次衣服
\item 你昨天喝了几次水？我昨天喝了十次水
\end{itemize}
\end{enumerate}
